url: "https://github.com/LIANJie-Jason/ai-surveillance-monitor"
repository-code: "https://github.com/LIANJie-Jason/ai-surveillance-monitor"
abstract: >-
  A real-time command center that tracks surveillance and censorship
  using AI-powered news analysis. Currently monitors 4 focus countries
  (India, Malaysia, Nigeria, South Africa) with plans to expand to full
  global coverage. Ingests RSS feeds from 64 sources, classifies articles
  with LLMs, and renders a live dashboard with a 3D rotating globe,
  country-level drill-downs, embedded news streams, and AI-generated
  article summaries.
keywords:
  - surveillance
  - censorship
  - computational repression
  - news monitoring
  - natural language processing
  - political science
